    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of September 17 article about effects of Firestone's tire recall on its competitors, which misstated name of Michelin North America marketing president Scott Clark (not Scott Blake) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article last Sunday about the effects of Firestone's tire recall on the business of its competitors misstated the surname of a vice president for marketing at one such company, Michelin North America. He is Scott Clark, not Scott Blake.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article last Sunday about the effects of Firestone's tire recall on the business of its competitors misstated the surname of a vice president for marketing at one such company, Michelin North America. He is Scott Clark, not Scott Blake.</p>
      </block>
